Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.23,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我叫中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.45,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,欢迎你的到来 葉香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:01:01.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是全球7G委员会会长 芃伊斯·庞太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:05.96,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,葉香小姐对能够以超级速度连接世界的7G网络有什么期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:09.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.00,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.24,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,无论何地 无论何人 都能快速被链接
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.80,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这就是梦想中的新技术 7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我们没赶上5G的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.64,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而6G却大器晚成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.51,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 我们终于用7G夺回日本国的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.98,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,虽然还是有些人反对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.14,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,甚至招来黑粉诽谤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是面对他们新闻学学的 我们没有退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:33.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界最先进强大的技术 全部都包含在7G里面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:37.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,采用全方位设备 直接将思想输入到大脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.62,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,思想马上传递 瞬间成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,堪比神明的力量 就是所谓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.31,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}那个 我能离开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:47.98,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就请大家一同见证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.68,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,通往未来的决定性时刻
