Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:40.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,黑豹车队即将到达吾野学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:47.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果您有快递 或是需要进行购物 请及时前往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.66,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,诶嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.66,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,这不是和代先生和御糸婆婆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.22,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,有啥奇怪的 我们俩在桥上碰见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.41,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我记得之前 你们不是为了一个麻袋吵了一架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,这种事情都过去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.46,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,难道你正治 还没有跟吉根她和好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.44,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 这倒也不全是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.95,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是不是还在抱怨她做的饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.03,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,她能给你做饭就不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:14.98,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,话是这么说 我是灰熊 她是赤麂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.70,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我们的口味真的天差地别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.88,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,口味？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.19,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,太小家子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.54,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.80,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,说到底 这还不是食物的问题嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.93,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.99,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,吾野可是很适合动物生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.20,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,我还听说有些地方的人 全都变成大树了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:29.74,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,大树？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.93,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,那边覆盖着群山的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.32,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,能变成动物还算我们幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.62,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.72,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,变成熊之后 我总是饿的好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,要是正治你变成一棵树就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.84,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,或者石头 蘑菇 还有铁线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.74,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,这话说的好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.39,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,习惯之后 作为动物的生活其实也并没有多糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.91,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,这点倒确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.10,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我都当了两年的熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.66,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,早就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.92,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,确实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.24,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,之前淳史变成指猴 一直都没适应过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.36,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,原来那天晚上 我看到的是淳史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.64,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,他已经长这么大了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.95,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他说要是知道会发生这种事 早就离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.80,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,无论走到哪里 在吾野的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.63,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,总会变成鸟类或是哺乳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.35,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.38,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,离不离开 都还是变成动物被困住 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.26,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.76,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,在7G事件发生前 失踪的那个女孩还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.01,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,她现在在哪里 做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.73,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,我记得那个叫千仓的女孩 还在寻找她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.30,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,先不说她在不在吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.57,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,但是她一个人独自在外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.02,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,兀自一人变成一个动物 可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.66,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,除了被动适应 还能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:32.42,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,至少不用再为健康保险和养老金发愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.37,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,再者说连诊所都没剩下几个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.05,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,所有的官僚早就灰飞烟灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.96,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,如果你现在走到稻荷山公园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.28,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,还是能在那找到一个非常好的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.10,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,不过这是我听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.70,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.67,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,谁知道你走过去 到底要花上几年时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.18,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,再说你还有没有命能活着到那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.34,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,还有 你都不知道它们是不是人类医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.52,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你是说人类的医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.13,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可能是给人类治病的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.80,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,也可能是「人类医生」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.87,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 你说它能给人治病 但却不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.02,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他不能给人类治病 但确仍是人类 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.10,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,那个在稻荷山的高明医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就好比是「咖喱味便便」那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我只是在问一个形而上学的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.09,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,女孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.19,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,说到咖喱 是不是肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.15,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,如果你们不介意 我可以分享一些蟋蟀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不用 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,现在吃点昆虫也没啥不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 一点也不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但听说很有营养
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,营养到不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自从那次事件后 我们每年能够收获六次大米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,更不用说大量的苦瓜 加上我每次摄入大量热量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,总之可爱与浪漫才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊又来了 逃避现实的情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,难道你是超·乐观主义 做梦酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我可是 知道你想说我什么哦 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你当我笨蛋 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不用谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,无论发生什么吵架绝对禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.54,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,被骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,被抚子姐骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.86,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}小晶你也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.57,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶真是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实也是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.50,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.81,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那个 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.07,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,黑豹车队来得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.62,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊 我们等了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的小灵通收到了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说明他们应该就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,难道黑豹车队全军覆灭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这下可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的杂志今天应该到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留她也不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这确实少见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,今天不是井口老师 对她进行前途职业咨询吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,前途 原来是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但现在讨论这个没啥意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.92,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,这些难过的话就别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,没啥没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.77,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这没有什么值得悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,全都是「现实」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.33,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 是善治郎先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野的标志性景观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.30,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他以前可是很高大英俊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.72,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,两年前他回吾野这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.14,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,就变成这样只会「吧吧」这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,善治郎特别之处 是还能保持人类模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他却只增加了二十一岁零三个月的年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,其它人却尽数变成了动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.74,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,噢 说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们最终 也会变成某种动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且还不能选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.59,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.60,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.63,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可是都等那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.39,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我可是好久没有吃肉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.01,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然肉更加好吃 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起米饭 甜番薯 还有苦瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.90,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.26,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,肉真的好好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.37,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我好想吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.99,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,牛排 鲜嫩 外加上几分生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.73,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不对 这超级稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.47,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可恶 我真想啃几口生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.27,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,等会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你这只食欲贪婪的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.74,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,诶 我刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正治先生 这样不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你完全变成熊的个性了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.27,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗…别开玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 放学之后的「加课」怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 加课？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 那完全问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.46,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他问了你的前途职业选择 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 他问我毕业之后想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说我要「寻找她」就被说教了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你说「寻找她」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.75,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.75,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,高先生 你是不是把它们占为己有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.24,ZH-Main-Down,Taka,0,0,0,,先到先得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.55,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,脑里只有吃肉没有别的 真无语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.58,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,看起来吾野这边又要大丰收了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.31,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,猫哥 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有什么消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.96,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,没有 这次又是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,传言呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比如镇上有新面孔 或是有人离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些传言有没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,这些传言也没听过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:17.00,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,能够与外面交流的沟通点并不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,如果有新的人出现 这种新闻肯定会马上传播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.01,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野这没有任何要报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我每天都在这里巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.23,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你们三人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.07,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你们想要的东西 我们终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的练马杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不知道这是二手书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有的看就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在根本没有新出版的书看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶 真的竟然找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,练马国的爱丽丝…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这就是杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,在7G事件之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:50.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这个节目一直都在埼玉电视台 每周四晚12：30分放送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.25,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这些超现实的毒药真的太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这也是可爱又浪漫的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们说的是同一档节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.52,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听我说 猫哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,请让我给你们打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.19,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,哈 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.46,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你说什么都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.60,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,这很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再者说我可是吾野柔道二段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.46,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,自从7G事件之后 熊是首先倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.42,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,之后便是鹈鹕 袋鼠 麋鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.01,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,剩下仅存的我们 虽然继续在送快递
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.97,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,但能坚持到什么时候也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,如果我有什么发现 肯定会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.26,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,好好耐心等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.51,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,就像我找到那本书一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.06,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,一切终将可能柳暗花明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不要总是想靠言语糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可恶 猫哥好难搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}他们走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还要再等一个月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,或者视情况等的时间会更多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:45.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子你买了什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.36,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是甜香桃木花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,甜…啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在还能生长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里能种的只有大米 小麦大麦 还有苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是无论如何 我很想要香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 为什么我突然会想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底是什么原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,问我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,甜香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞 我想是以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以小晶你买了什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,作者龙彦 黑魔法书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,龙彦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,说起龙彦肯定是指涩泽龙彦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,谁会那么肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么了 静留姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,竟然还有出版的新报纸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,「钻石之门逐渐放大」上面写着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个人 难道不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香 真的是葉香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈 这个葉香是那个葉香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有谁能叫葉香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说是上个月的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全无法相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她为什么会在池袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要告诉小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:01.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,两年前的那一天 世界完全改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,火车站之间的距离 城镇之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然增加到无法跨越的长度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是地理的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所有人和生物都发生了彻底的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在吾野的成年人都变成了动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然现在还保留有人类的理性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:24.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但总可能有一天 会变成真正的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是吾野的情况 或许更加严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初的时候大家都被震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己变成了奇怪的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,愤怒 自暴自弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一些人组成调查小组 冒险前往别处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一半的人中途放弃折返回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的一半人再也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:10.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这可能是 她刚知道自己唯一的孙女还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,太高兴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶也没能变能更年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,豚鼠要再过五六年可能会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:17.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么小晶你要说这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是玲实你提到她的年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是真的神经大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我只是要教你一些知识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}要好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.55,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:47.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些一切现象的变化 都是7G网络失控所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 没有人知道如何将这一切改变回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者说 我感觉并没有人想要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我做好了晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,虽然还是一如既往的苦瓜和米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,但你可要先加热后再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:12.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,电器之类的 应该说该感谢7G还是该谴责 总之功不可没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:17.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们无法看电视或是上网 只有小灵通近距离能用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冰箱虽然还在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是冰箱和微波炉同时用会跳闸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们不能像以前一样随意地使用电能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,甚至说这到底是不是电能 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:34.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,它更像一种能量 沿着类似铁轨传导
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来静留 你是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你那么惊讶干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你也是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:52.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你说什么抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本不知道 葉香你到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她到底什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那晚之后 再也没见过葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也再也没碰见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且我也没有找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怪不得我找不到她 原来她在池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还以为她就在吾野附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还苦苦寻找她了两年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:25.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说波奇 为什么你没有变成人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,既然所有人长大后都会变成动物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那波奇变成了人类也就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果葉香就在附近 波奇应该也会告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟她是你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我怎么从来都没有注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.30,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生 你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站在这种地方可是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.94,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,帽 帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,母子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:04.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子的丝带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 这个是什么知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎 那边很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里面有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吧吧的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.80,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那个可恶该死的庞太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.03,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我说了多少次要他放弃7G
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.86,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,根本不可能有人采用这种标准的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.27,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,威胁到物理定律 无视研究人员警告 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.28,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,只盲目接受「牟利者」提供的不可靠数据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.38,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,而且为什么不采用下策 非要采用下下策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.68,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,真的是可恶的没用废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.30,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你不仅阻挡了我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.45,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,还用软绵绵让我变得软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.75,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,真的是不可原谅的狡猾恶徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.55,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你给我洗好屁股等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.50,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我绝对要把7G停给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.87,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不会让你霸占池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等会 你说池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.16,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.89,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我不能就这样离开池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.17,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我要马上去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.31,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,看起来只有让我平善次郎驾驶这辆两千系列…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.96,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不对 等 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你是 千仓静留对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.42,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你小的时候跌到泥沟里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎样都行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,重要的是你是如何把两千系列带出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你会开火车吗 善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你说我会不会开火车？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.91,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咋了咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,给我再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 真的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么帽子突然又不能把他变回来 不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,尽你所能 要确保自身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谢谢你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,如果路途中遇见了一直傲慢的狼獾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,记得叫他振作起来 快点回家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我会如实告诉父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.49,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,星抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.17,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,九贺玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:26.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.25,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,东云晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:28.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.45,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,中富葉香 请假缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.76,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,千仓静留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.19,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,静留她又逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.50,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,你们三人都不知道她在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,前天晚上 她说她解开了帽子谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以她围着吾野学校跑步 和波奇一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什么谜团？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等会 她逃课在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不良？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留变成不良少女了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.94,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,在这里做不良行为毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.14,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,所以我认为不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,井口老师 多谢您的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要退学啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:01.90,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.25,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.24,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我虽然无法和你一起去 但看起来你没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.65,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,走出这里 去看看被7G所破坏的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.47,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我会等着你的回复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:18.06,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,听好 最重要的是保证自己的生存…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 又是半途而废到关键点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我大概明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:25.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}根本不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你已经吓我们一大跳了 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你到底为啥要退学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,之后就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我现在就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:39.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这可并不突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我可是好好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哇 竟然动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是吧 敲 开玩笑啊
